  <entry>
    <title>GroupBy - 資料分群的收納師</title>
    <url>/2024/03/17/Therapy-for-Our-Data-LINQ-GropuBy/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="MS-Doc-名詞解析"><a href="#MS-Doc-名詞解析" class="headerlink" title="MS Doc 名詞解析"></a>MS Doc 名詞解析</h2><p><code>keySelector</code> : 要使用什麼屬性(or欄位)做分組 </p>
<p><code>comparer</code>： 客製的等值比較器，這裡是比較key是否相同來決定要不要分在同一組</p>
<p><code>elementSelector</code> : 參數是針對分組中的元素,使用前還沒有得到分組後的結果</p>
<p><code>resultSelector</code> : 參數是針對分組結果再進一步進行資料結構的轉換</p>
<p><code>IEnumerable&lt;System.Linq.IGrouping&lt;TKey,TSource&gt;&gt;</code> : 分組後的資料</p>
<p><code>IEnumerable&lt;TSource&gt;</code> : 資料源</p>
<h2 id="MS-Doc-範例"><a href="#MS-Doc-範例" class="headerlink" title="MS Doc 範例"></a>MS Doc 範例</h2><p>這個情境會對分組後的資料動手腳,就不需要在後面處理<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/2BeCpkd.png" alt="Image"><br>在此,GroupBy只把所需的名字抓出來，所以在做處理時不用再從Pet中找出Name資料了，相對精簡<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/q4IOyAZ.png" alt="Image"></p>
<h2 id="情境一"><a href="#情境一" class="headerlink" title="情境一."></a>情境一.</h2><p>按價格範圍對訂單進行分組</p>
<figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Main</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    List&lt;Order&gt; orders = <span class="keyword">new</span> List&lt;Order&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">1</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">150</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">2</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">50</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">3</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">20</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">4</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">500</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">5</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">80</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">6</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">200</span>m &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">new</span> Order &#123; OrderId = <span class="number">7</span>, TotalAmount = <span class="number">700</span>m &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> groupOrders = orders.GroupBy(order =&gt; </span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> order.TotalAmount <span class="keyword">switch</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">decimal</span> amount <span class="keyword">when</span> amount &lt; <span class="number">100</span> =&gt; <span class="string">&quot;Small Order&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">decimal</span> amount <span class="keyword">when</span> amount &gt;= <span class="number">100</span> &amp;&amp; amount &lt;= <span class="number">500</span> =&gt; <span class="string">&quot;Medium Order&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            _ =&gt; <span class="string">&quot;Large Order&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">foreach</span>(<span class="keyword">var</span> <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> groupOrders)</span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">group</span>.Key.Dump();</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">foreach</span>(<span class="keyword">var</span> order <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="keyword">group</span>)</span><br><span class="line">		&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="string">$&quot;OrderId : <span class="subst">&#123;order.OrderId&#125;</span>, TotalAmount : <span class="subst">&#123;order.TotalAmount&#125;</span>&quot;</span>.Dump();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>.Dump();</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Order</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">int</span> OrderId &#123; <span class="keyword">get</span>; <span class="keyword">set</span>; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">decimal</span> TotalAmount &#123; <span class="keyword">get</span>; <span class="keyword">set</span>; &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="情境二"><a href="#情境二" class="headerlink" title="情境二."></a>情境二.</h2><p>拆成批次作業</p>
<figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Main</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> random = <span class="keyword">new</span> Random();</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">string</span>[] MainStrings = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">string</span>[<span class="number">50</span>];</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="built_in">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; MainStrings.Length; i++)</span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">var</span> radnomString = GenerateRandomString(random);</span><br><span class="line">		MainStrings[i] = radnomString;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	IEnumerable&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span>&gt; mainStrings = MainStrings.AsEnumerable();</span><br><span class="line">	IEnumerable&lt;IEnumerable&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span>&gt;&gt; chuncks = mainStrings.Chunk(<span class="number">10</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">foreach</span>(<span class="keyword">var</span> chunck <span class="keyword">in</span> chuncks)</span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		chunck.Select(c =&gt; c).Dump();</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">IEnumerableExtension</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="title">IEnumerable</span>&lt;<span class="title">IEnumerable</span>&lt;<span class="title">TSource</span>&gt;&gt; <span class="title">Chunk</span>&lt;<span class="title">TSource</span>&gt;(<span class="params"><span class="keyword">this</span> IEnumerable&lt;TSource&gt; source, <span class="built_in">int</span> size</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (source == <span class="literal">null</span> || source.Any() == <span class="literal">false</span>)</span><br><span class="line">		&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">return</span> Enumerable.Empty&lt;IEnumerable&lt;TSource&gt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">var</span> result = source.Select((x, i) =&gt; <span class="keyword">new</span> &#123; Index = i, Value = x &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">						   .GroupBy(e =&gt; e.Index / size)</span><br><span class="line">						   .Select(g =&gt; g.Select(e =&gt; e.Value));</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">return</span> result;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="built_in">string</span> <span class="title">GenerateRandomString</span>(<span class="params">Random random</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">// 字元寶典</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">char</span>[] characters = <span class="string">&quot;abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ0123456789&quot;</span>.ToCharArray();</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">//隨機取一個string想要的長度</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> length = random.Next(<span class="number">10</span>,<span class="number">20</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">// 空字串</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> goodString = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="built_in">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span> ; i &lt; length ; i++)</span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">var</span> charac = characters[random.Next(characters.Length)];</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">		goodString += charac;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> goodString;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
